---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import IconHeart from "../components/Icons/IconHeart.svelte";
import IconGitHubSponsors from "../components/Icons/IconGitHubSponsors.svelte";
import IconOpenCollective from "../components/Icons/IconOpenCollective.svelte";
import IconStripe from "../components/Icons/IconStripe.svelte";
import HoverCardLink from "../components/Sponsorships/HoverCardLink.svelte";
---

<Layout
  title="Sponsorship | coolLabs"
  canonicalUrl="https://coolify.io/sponsorships/"
  description="Support Coolify's development. Sponsor us on GitHub or Open Collective to keep the project free and accessible for everyone."
>
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white md:text-6xl px-4">
    Sponsor Us<span class="text-warning">.</span>
  </h1>
  <h2 class="text-base pb-10 pt-2 text-neutral-400 px-4">
    We love doing open-source projects.
    <IconHeart class="w-6 h-6 inline-block text-pink-400" />
  </h2>

  <div class="pt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-left text-neutral-400">
      We are a self-funded company and depend on your support to sustain the
      project. This allows for a focus on real users (like you) rather than on
      investors or revenue. If you opt for our self-hosted version, you have the
      option to support our work through donations.
    </div>
  </div>

  <div
    class="pt-10 pb-2 flex lg:flex-row flex-col items-center justify-center text-center gap-8 px-4"
  >
    <a
      href="https://github.com/sponsors/coollabsio"
      target="_blank"
      class="button flex items-center gap-4 w-64 justify-center"
    >
      <IconGitHubSponsors class="w-10 h-10 text-white" />
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <span>GitHub Sponsors</span>
        <span class="text-xs text-gray-400">Donation</span>
      </div></a
    >
    <a
      href="https://opencollective.com/coollabsio/donate?interval=month&amount=10&name=&legalName=&email="
      target="_blank"
      class="button flex items-center gap-4 w-64 justify-center"
    >
      <IconOpenCollective class="w-10 h-10 text-white" />
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <span>Open Collective</span>
        <span class="text-xs text-gray-400">Donation</span>
      </div>
    </a>
    <a
      href="https://donate.stripe.com/8x2bJ104ifmB9kB45u38402"
      target="_blank"
      class="button flex items-center gap-4 w-64 justify-center"
    >
      <IconStripe class="w-10 h-10 text-white" />
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <span>Stripe</span>
        <span class="text-xs text-gray-400">Donation</span>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>

  <div class="pt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center text-neutral-400">
      You can even get free visitors (170k+ unique visitors per month - landing
      page, docs, Github readme...) to your project, by buying a slot.
      <br/><br/>
      <div class="text-center">
        <HoverCardLink
          client:load
          href="https://github.com/sponsors/coollabsio/sponsorships?tier_id=61570&preview=false"
          label="Small"
          newTab={true}
          warning={true}
          card={{
            kind: "sponsor",
            tierName: "Small Sponsor",
            amount: 40,
            description: "Small logo + link on the front page and on GitHub README."
          }}
        />, a
        <HoverCardLink
          client:load
          href="https://github.com/sponsors/coollabsio/sponsorships?tier_id=334953&preview=false"
          label="large"
          newTab={true}
          warning={true}
          card={{
            kind: "sponsor",
            tierName: "Large Sponsor",
            amount: 200,
            description: "Larger logo + link on the front page and on GitHub README."
          }}
        /> or a
        <HoverCardLink
          client:load
          href="https://github.com/sponsors/coollabsio/sponsorships?tier_id=554249&preview=false"
          label="huge"
          newTab={true}
          warning={true}
          card={{
            kind: "sponsor",
            tierName: "Huge Sponsor",
            amount: 500,
            description: "Huge logo (featured) + link on the front page and on GitHub README."
          }}
        /> logo + link on the front page and on Github README.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h3
    class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white md:text-3xl pt-16 px-4"
  >
    Who Is Behind This<span class="text-warning">?</span>
  </h3>
  <h4 class="text-base pb-10 pt-2 text-neutral-400 px-4">
    A one-person mission that grew into a team.
  </h4>

  <div class="pt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 pb-8">
    <div class="text-left text-neutral-400">
      Hey, I'm
      <HoverCardLink
        client:load
        href="https://twitter.com/heyandras"
        label="Andras Bacsai"
        showExternalIcon={true}
        newTab={true}
        card={{
          kind: "twitter",
          name: "Andras Bacsai",
          username: "heyandras",
          bio: "Entrepreneur, 2 x dad, 💜 OSS & simplicity.",
          website: "coolify.io / jean.build / ideas.coollabs.io",
          joined: "Joined December 2013",
          avatarUrl: "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2049068753334452224/vSOyoJ6X_400x400.jpg",
          followers: 23900,
          following: 494
        }}
      />
      <br /><br />
      I'm a software developer based in Hungary who shifted to being an independent
      entrepreneur in July 2022. I quit my job to focus entirely on my dream of devoting
      myself to open-source projects.
      <br /><br />
      Since the middle of 2024, I'm not the only one working on these projects. Thanks
      to the sponsors and paid users, I hired a developer and a few community support
      members who help me with the projects.
      <br /><br />
      If you find my open-source projects helpful or value my work, please think about
      making a
      <HoverCardLink
        client:load
        href="https://github.com/sponsors/coollabsio"
        label="donation or sponsoring"
        newTab={true}
        card={{
          kind: "github-sponsor",
          name: "coollabsio",
          username: "coollabsio",
          bio: "Cool Labs is an independent open-source company that builds and maintains open-source projects like Coolify.",
          sponsorCount: 304,
          imageUrl: "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/60715044?s=160&v=4"
        }}
      />.
      <br /><br />
      This will guarantee that the projects stay free, accessible, and keep developing,
      enabling me to devote all my time to creating and enhancing them.
      <br /><br />
      It provides me with significant long-term benefits!
      <br /><br />
      Thank you!
    </div>

  </div>
</Layout>
